{"tid":1369150,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"班狗已經俾我地趕左入窮巷  就黎狗急跳牆","createTime":"2019-07-26T15:37:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T17:54:47.000Z","uid":1251,"like":56,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"072128bee9883234f7966c1c5f7295264e92950c","tid":1369150,"uid":1251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T15:37:54.000Z","msg":"好快政府就會當佢地係condom咁用完即棄<br />\n<br />\n今次同雨傘唔同<br />\n如果冇特別事發生<br />\n民意係唔會拖拖下消耗<br />\n因為大部份香港人都憤怒到極點<br />\n連公務員都企出黎<br />\n地鐵車長都話罷駛<br />\n建制都排隊割蓆<br />\n政府同狗都鬧翻<br />\n形勢已經唔同左<br />\n<br />\n雖然未贏<br />\n但唔駛心急<br />\n睇定先行動<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">聽日我會去元朗食糯米糍<br />\n唔捉鬼唔割蓆<br />\n但有人衝我一定會阻止<br />\n帶佢一齊去食花生糯米糍<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"5a7d8172305709bad4386e7f4ee1cf4e1c4545a3","tid":1369150,"uid":1251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T15:39:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"041cde1067c7f028abbf4a7d53b9551f98cc7170","tid":1369150,"uid":276440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T15:40:48.000Z","msg":"香港人加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b052b5b12fd221c697f45243ee48b04ed3942192","tid":1369150,"uid":1251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T15:41:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdc55d1bec06960fc76b316edd747d6d7a7d4e10","tid":1369150,"uid":1251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T15:43:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkg